3cb5a76e-ce73-4955-ad22-af8458cdb80e.title: Note
3cb5a76e-ce73-4955-ad22-af8458cdb80e.text: Probably missing dialogue for both MINING & SMITHING

03f0d934-56aa-40ac-af74-2eaa9798b282.title: Mining Instructor
03f0d934-56aa-40ac-af74-2eaa9798b282.text:
Hi there. You must be new around here. So what do I
call you? 'Newcomer' seems so impersonal, and if we're
going to be working together, I'd rather call you by
name.

6e937aa3-f54f-42ed-966a-a5368754422b.title: Mining Instructor
6e937aa3-f54f-42ed-966a-a5368754422b.text:
Ok then, <player>. My name is Dezzick and I'm a
miner by trade. Let's look at some of those rocks.

2fe4e373-2b22-49f1-8a93-19e404c47097.title: Mining Instructor
2fe4e373-2b22-49f1-8a93-19e404c47097.text:
One set contains tin and the other has copper ore inside.
These two ore types can be smelted together
to make bronze.

aca4a2fd-d82b-4215-ae12-68af435667ad.title: Mining Instructor
aca4a2fd-d82b-4215-ae12-68af435667ad.text:
So now you know what ore is in the rocks over there,
why don't you have a go at mining some tin and
copper? Here, you'll need this to start with.

a0f37326-e02a-4245-b824-dac9884bc74b.title: <player>
a0f37326-e02a-4245-b824-dac9884bc74b.text: How do i make a weapon out of this?

8fa7017d-7804-42ae-ad0a-856b730c5a32.title: Mining Instructor
8fa7017d-7804-42ae-ad0a-856b730c5a32.text:
Okay, I'll show you how to make a dagger out of it.
You'll be needing this...

args: Smelt the ore, then use the anvil.

options.text: Nope, I'm ready to move on!
